Action chain (any callback returning truthy short-circuits):
  1. dobj OBJECT-FUNCTION pre-phase
{% if arity == 2 %}  2. iobj OBJECT-FUNCTION pre-phase
{% endif %}  {% if arity == 2 %}3{% else %}2{% endif %}. ROOM-FUNCTION M-BEG
  {% if arity == 2 %}4{% else %}3{% endif %}. Substrate verb: _.thing.{{ substrate_verb }}()
  {% if arity == 2 %}5{% else %}4{% endif %}. ROOM-FUNCTION M-END

Option A delegation: the substrate is rewritten to ``--dspec none`` by
the generator's post-emission pass so it never parser-matches; this
runner is the only parser entry point, and it calls the substrate
programmatically via :func:`invoke_verb` to preserve hand-written
